{"tid":1824391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大核彈!!金管局外匯儲備4個月唔見左5500億!!","createTime":"2020-01-14T11:35:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T13:34:18.000Z","uid":327767,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"67195da6db7bf116e66a7e5439b9b3f035ce4155","tid":1824391,"uid":327767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T11:35:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkma.gov.hk/chi/news-and-media/press-releases/2019/09/20190930-6/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkma.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fnews-and-media%2Fpress-releases%2F2019%2F09%2F20190930-6%2F&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSern6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=87d0aa2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkma.gov.hk/chi/news-and-media/press-releases/2019/09/20190930-6/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港金融管理局（金管局）今日（星期一）公布，截至2019年8月31日，外匯基金總資產達41,629億港元，較2019年7月底增加253億港元，其中外幣資產增加402億港元，港元資產則減少149億港元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkma.gov.hk/chi/news-and-media/press-releases/2020/01/20200107-4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkma.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fnews-and-media%2Fpress-releases%2F2020%2F01%2F20200107-4%2F&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSern6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=eb2fcbf1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkma.gov.hk/chi/news-and-media/press-releases/2020/01/20200107-4/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港金融管理局（金管局）今日（星期二）公布外匯基金在2019年12月底的主要分析帳目。<br />\n<br />\n在12月份，外匯基金的境外資產增加383億港元，至36,173億港元。<br />\n<br />\n貨幣基礎為16,624億港元，包括負債證明書、政府發行的流通紙幣及硬幣、銀行體系結餘，以及已發行外匯基金票據及債券。<br />\n<br />\n=================================<br />\n<br />\n有無做金融吧巴打解釋有咩原因?撤資?定根本自動轉賬比老共買豆?<br />\n4個月唔見5500億,以呢個速度計算,2年後3.6萬億可以蒸發哂....<br />\n唔洗借明日大嶼,唔洗過立法會,呢招空手入白刃夠直接<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢件事一定一定要撤查,如果真係老共係幕後黑手一定要煲到最大,<br />\n到時睇吓你D外資仲留唔留低做韮菜?"},{"pid":"5345e41de7e4cca74bbb93e4df9e6b0ba53777a7","tid":1824391,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T11:38:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b04443c7abd9edc1c92faa467853ef8fc5bd385","tid":1824391,"uid":257368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T11:38:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201912/31/P2019123100299.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201912%2F31%2FP2019123100299.htm&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSern6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=8ac05136\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201912/31/P2019123100299.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n境外資產=總資產？"},{"pid":"be41e941fbffc67c81a4c5dabbb7d462c03e1131","tid":1824391,"uid":327767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b04443c7abd9edc1c92faa467853ef8fc5bd385","tid":1824391,"uid":257368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T11:38:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201912/31/P2019123100299.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201912%2F31%2FP2019123100299.htm&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSern6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=8ac05136\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201912/31/P2019123100299.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n境外資產=總資產？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T11:41:39.000Z","msg":"柒到喊左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n此POST已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e93f16ed5797dd2963ba6e763f67d267add4c37","tid":1824391,"uid":30737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T11:43:45.000Z","msg":"巴打，一個係總資產，一個係境外資產...."},{"pid":"8e68b118c979d42b08d954a729248c9dfe9b8da8","tid":1824391,"uid":327767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2e93f16ed5797dd2963ba6e763f67d267add4c37","tid":1824391,"uid":30737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T11:43:45.000Z","msg":"巴打，一個係總資產，一個係境外資產...."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T11:50:31.000Z","msg":"收到，麻煩幫我搵個窿捐吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36eab9957c97f6ce477ae7907da07b6c88a80824","tid":1824391,"uid":266755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T12:38:07.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"27c67d1ffd0cbc0e13d55f83145701a0066fa10d","tid":1824391,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:19:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d9abbd8e77276f4e84944764b27f275d738a052","tid":1824391,"uid":327767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"27c67d1ffd0cbc0e13d55f83145701a0066fa10d","tid":1824391,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:19:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:23:02.000Z","msg":"係我學藝未精、係我自曝其短，我應該讀多D書，我知錯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a06a10c7aebbc41fa5e2ef36b5957866bdf0d7","tid":1824391,"uid":34594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:27:10.000Z","msg":"幫拉"},{"pid":"bd4f0a4f93756115e01b595cca33108331e261da","tid":1824391,"uid":239689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:27:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed4d5458ff859b1d046efacb1bcaeffdb71854f1","tid":1824391,"uid":321803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"67195da6db7bf116e66a7e5439b9b3f035ce4155","tid":1824391,"uid":327767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T11:35:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkma.gov.hk/chi/news-and-media/press-releases/2019/09/20190930-6/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkma.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fnews-and-media%2Fpress-releases%2F2019%2F09%2F20190930-6%2F&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSern6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=87d0aa2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkma.gov.hk/chi/news-and-media/press-releases/2019/09/20190930-6/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港金融管理局（金管局）今日（星期一）公布，截至2019年8月31日，外匯基金總資產達41,629億港元，較2019年7月底增加253億港元，其中外幣資產增加402億港元，港元資產則減少149億港元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkma.gov.hk/chi/news-and-media/press-releases/2020/01/20200107-4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkma.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fnews-and-media%2Fpress-releases%2F2020%2F01%2F20200107-4%2F&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSern6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=eb2fcbf1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkma.gov.hk/chi/news-and-media/press-releases/2020/01/20200107-4/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港金融管理局（金管局）今日（星期二）公布外匯基金在2019年12月底的主要分析帳目。<br />\n<br />\n在12月份，外匯基金的境外資產增加383億港元，至36,173億港元。<br />\n<br />\n貨幣基礎為16,624億港元，包括負債證明書、政府發行的流通紙幣及硬幣、銀行體系結餘，以及已發行外匯基金票據及債券。<br />\n<br />\n=================================<br />\n<br />\n有無做金融吧巴打解釋有咩原因?撤資?定根本自動轉賬比老共買豆?<br />\n4個月唔見5500億,以呢個速度計算,2年後3.6萬億可以蒸發哂....<br />\n唔洗借明日大嶼,唔洗過立法會,呢招空手入白刃夠直接<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢件事一定一定要撤查,如果真係老共係幕後黑手一定要煲到最大,<br />\n到時睇吓你D外資仲留唔留低做韮菜?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:34:18.000Z","msg":"無問題，睇緊啲緊張好正常"}]}